# Custom Logic üõ†Ô∏è

Create your own directives for low-level DOM access.

Example: `v-focus` to focus an input on mount.

```javascript
app.directive('focus', {
  mounted(el) {
    el.focus()
  }
})
```
Usage: `<input v-focus />`

